## Helper Decorators
PropertyPlus also embraces a new notation for Property descriptors.  
This optional feature is purely stylistic, but we like it.

### getter(prop)

### setter(prop)

### deleter(prop)

### validator(prop)

### normalizer(prop)

### typefixer(prop)
